    <!-- ABOUT -->

    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>About Soochna Mandir</h2>

        <p>
            Soochna Mandir is an independent technology-enabled platform focused
            on publicly available civic and community information.
        </p>

        <p>
            The platform supports public communication, citizen assistance,
            information accessibility, and civic awareness initiatives through
            digital systems and modern communication tools.
        </p>

        <p>
            Soochna Mandir operates independently and is not affiliated with
            government agencies.
        </p>

    </section>

